  <brief_title>Efficacy Study of Topical Twice Weekly Fluticasone Treatment to Reduce Relapse in Atopic Dermatitis in Children</brief_title>
  <official_title>Randomised Controlled, Double Blind Trial of Topical Twice Weekly Fluticasone Propionate Maintenance Treatment to Reduce Risk of Relapse in Mild or Moderate Atopic Dermatitis in Children</official_title>
